{"title":"Forbidden’s GX Druid Ziggy Edition is made-to-mullet w/ included Ziggy Link","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/06/14/forbiddens-gx-druid-ziggy-edition-is-made-to-mullet-w-included-ziggy-link/","date":1623686425000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Business up front, party in the back! While it’s never been the best recipe for hair, it seems to be working for a lot of mountain bikers. As more and more riders are showing an interest in mixed wheel setups, Forbidden Bike Co. has released a complete Druid that boasts a mullet build right out of the box.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155852/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-link-on-bike.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155852/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-link-on-bike.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb18/ng:webp/ngcb18\" alt=\"Forbidden GX Druid Ziggy Edition, link on bike\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155852/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-link-on-bike.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155852/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-link-on-bike-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155852/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-link-on-bike-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155852/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-link-on-bike-768x513.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155852/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-link-on-bike-696x465.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/n