as introduced as a mullet conversion kit for the Druids (FYI – it also works for Forbidden’s new Dreadnought frames).</p><figure id=\"attachment_261776\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-261776\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-scaled.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"Forbidden GX Druid Ziggy Edition, geo chart\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1269\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-scaled.jpg 2560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-297x147.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-800x396.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-120x59.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-768x381.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-1536x761.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-2048x1015.jpg 2048w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-696x345.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-1068x529.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-1920x951.jpg 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-848x420.jpg 848w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-324x160.jpg 324w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb18 src ng ngcb18 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-scaled.jpg 2560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-297x147.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-800x396.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-120x59.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-768x381.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-1536x761.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-2048x1015.jpg 2048w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-696x345.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-1068x529.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-1920x951.jpg 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-848x420.jpg 848w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155839/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-geometry-324x160.jpg 324w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-261776\">*Click to see larger image</figcaption></figure><p>Replacing the rear suspension’s lower link, the Ziggy Link doesn’t just allow the smaller rear wheel to fit the frame while retaining the same geometry – Forbidden decided the link should alter the frame geo to best suit the mixed wheel setup. Accordingly, the Ziggy Link drops the Druid’s BB by 4mm and slackens the head tube angle by 0.5°.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155858/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-side.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155858/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-side.jpg\" alt=\"Forbidden GX Druid Ziggy Edition, side\" width=\"800\" height=\"507\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155858/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-side.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155858/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-side-297x188.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155858/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-side-120x76.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155858/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-side-768x487.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155858/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-side-696x441.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155858/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-side-663x420.jpg 663w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb18 src ng ngcb18 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155858/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-side.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155858/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-side.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155858/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-side-297x188.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155858/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-side-120x76.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155858/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-side-768x487.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155858/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-side-696x441.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155858/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-side-663x420.jpg 663w\"></a></p><p>While they adjusted the bike’s geometry, Forbidden designed the Ziggy Link so it does not change the suspension kinematics. Riders should enjoy the same suspension feel and ride qualities through the bike’s 130mm travel whether they’re running a 29” or 27.5” wheel out back.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155847/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-linkage-drivetrain.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155847/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-linkage-drivetrain.jpg\" alt=\"Forbidden GX Druid Ziggy Edition, drivetrain/linkage\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155847/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-linkage-drivetrain.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155847/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-linkage-drivetrain-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155847/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-linkage-drivetrain-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155847/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-linkage-drivetrain-768x513.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155847/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-linkage-drivetrain-696x465.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155847/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-linkage-drivetrain-629x420.jpg 629w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb18 src ng ngcb18 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155847/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-linkage-drivetrain.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155847/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-linkage-drivetrain.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155847/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-linkage-drivetrain-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155847/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-linkage-drivetrain-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155847/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-linkage-drivetrain-768x513.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155847/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-linkage-drivetrain-696x465.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155847/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-linkage-drivetrain-629x420.jpg 629w\"></a></p><p>The GX Druid Ziggy Edition will be sold with one complete mid-level build spec. See the chart for all the details but some highlights include a Shimano GX drivetrain, SRAM G2 RSC 4-piston brakes, Crankbrothers Synthesis Enduro alloy wheels, and a set of Maxxis Assegai/Minion tires.</p><figure id=\"attachment_261780\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-261780\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155903/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-specs.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155903/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-specs.jpg\" alt=\"Forbidden GX Druid Ziggy Edition, build specs\" width=\"2009\" height=\"1326\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155903/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-specs.jpg 2009w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/13155903/Forbidden-GX-Druid-Ziggy-Edition-specs-297x196.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bike